[31/12/2016 21:46:02] <font color="#ffffff">¿Sí?</font>
[31/12/2016 21:46:05] <font color="#ffffff">Hola, Geanine.</font>
[31/12/2016 21:46:05] <font color="#ffffff">Hola, chef.</font>
[31/12/2016 21:46:07] <font color="#ffffff">Bórdele el nombre debajo del Cargo.</font>
